{"tid":1682631,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我們之間，是三樓與九樓的距離","createTime":"2019-10-30T07:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:39:08.000Z","uid":33419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6165a239dd084412eb7c54a18af5666fdaa3ccd","tid":1682631,"uid":33419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"「Falling in love,Falling in love<br />\n    Deeper than I&rsquo;ve felt it before with you, baby 」<br />\n耳機聽著Cigarettes After Sex 的 Falling In Love，眼中突然出現你的身影<br />\n雙馬尾碎花短裙，蕾絲短襪加上皮鞋，背著深藍色的背囊<br />\n前後走著走著，步伐慢慢變得一致<br />\n你看著前方的男孩打開大廈的門，急得輕快跑上前<br />\n「快消失了，要追上嗎？」<br />\n「算吧...反正不會坐同一架升降機」<br />\n<br />\n我伸手拉著門，踏著平日的步伐，走向升降機<br />\n突然，看到你按著開門鍵，微微一笑，多麼可愛...<br />\n「Thank y... 」喉嚨突然乾起來！是太緊張了嗎？<br />\n是九樓！三樓與九樓之間的距離<br />\n「Back when you were far away<br />\nWe would go on dates to watch the same movie<br />\n&amp; you were imagining sitting next to me<br />\n&amp; holding my hand for the whole thing&hellip;」<br />\n那一瞬間，想過很多種可能<br />\n<br />\n叮叮...三樓，Third floor，門徐徐打開<br />\n「到了...唉」我拿著鎖匙包，慢步走出<br />\n到最後也沒有回頭......<br />\n<br />\n如果你看到這篇文，如果下次我們再相遇，我...可以認識你嗎？<br />\n記 2019年10月29日 晚上11時左右<br />\n致那短暫的瞬間，停駐在我心間的妳"},{"pid":"1491c9293555d396011f6ea6e8f988616e88fee0","tid":1682631,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xTYJ2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xTYJ2h.jpg&h=cd8db3a4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b477ba6d2cd2c88c94fdbce2baf0d28f498691bb","tid":1682631,"uid":33419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"2cc2afb64d75e68806fad48090b74ff129fddd89","tid":1682631,"uid":33419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"a218d5d88bb71071cb2979e1bdeda7fe6d1a9f14","tid":1682631,"uid":33419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite